<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-3171] AbstractCompactionIterable uses a 1MB buffer for every sstable</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-3171</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This causes an OOM for any compaction task that needs to open all the sstables when you have a lot of them (repair, major, etc)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12522467">CASSANDRA-3171</key>
            <summary>AbstractCompactionIterable uses a 1MB buffer for every sstable</summary>
